title: Katarina in a Katsuit
body:
https://i.imgur.com/9DMPrsR.png[/img]

Originally I was going for Pentakill Katarina, but I never ended up adding any spikes or metal and decided she looked better without them. So it didn't turn out pentakill-y at all lol. So, for lack of a better title: Katarina in a Katsuit
